OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FA member of a South African research
OL,7,Fteam at a remote base in Antarctica
OL,8,Fhas been placed under psychological
OL,9,Fevaluation there after he allegedly
OL,10,Fassaulted and sexually harassed
OL,11,Fcolleagues, government officials said.
OL,13,FIt comes after a group of his
OL,14,Fcolleagues asked for "immediate
OL,15,Faction" after a member of their team
OL,16,Fallegedly physically assaulted and
OL,17,Fthreatened to kill another colleague.
