OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FThe researchers are in total isolation
OL,7,Fat South Africa's Sanae IV base, and
OL,8,Fare reported to have ten months left
OL,9,Fof their 16 month expedition.
OL,11,FLocated in the Queen Maud Land region,
OL,12,Fthe base is 80 kilometres inland on a
OL,13,Fnunatak - a mountain ridge that
OL,14,Fprotrudes from a glacier - and is
OL,15,Fcompletely surrounded by glacial sheet.
OL,17,FIts remote location combined with
OL,18,Fextreme weather conditions can make it
OL,19,Fdifficult to reach.
