OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,F"Furthermore, he threatened to kill
OL,7,F(name withheld), creating an
OL,8,Fenvironment of fear and intimidation.
OL,9,FI remain deeply concerned about my own
OL,10,Fsafety, constantly wondering if I
OL,11,Fmight become the next victim."
OL,13,FThe researcher said the team member
OL,14,Fhad also been accused of sexual
OL,15,Fassault, adding that his behaviour had
OL,16,Fbecome "increasingly egregious".
OL,18,F"It is imperative that immediate
OL,19,Faction is taken to ensure my safety
OL,20,Fand the safety of all employees," the
OL,21,Fmessage continued.
