OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,F"You can imagine what it's like, it is
OL,7,Fclose quarters and people do get cabin
OL,8,Ffever. It can be very disorientating."
OL,10,FWatch: A tour around South Africa's
OL,11,FSanae IV base posted four years ago
OL,13,FBecause of the conditions at the base,
OL,14,FGeorge said that researchers undergo
OL,15,Fpsychometric assessments before
OL,16,Fdeployment.
OL,18,FThe base has three modules and
OL,19,Fincludes a helicopter hanger, sauna
OL,20,Fand hospital.
