OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FThe nine-member team, which includes
OL,7,Fscientists, a doctor and engineers, is
OL,8,Fexpected to stay at the base for about
OL,9,F13 months until next year, authorities
OL,10,Fsaid, living in close quarters through
OL,11,Fthe hostile Antarctic winter, whose
OL,12,Fsix months of darkness begin in June.
OL,14,FPrevious problems have been reported
OL,15,Fat another of South Africa's remote
OL,16,Fresearch bases on Marion Island, a
OL,17,FSouth African territory near
OL,18,FAntarctica.
