OL,3,CTrapped researchers in Antarctica call
OL,4,Cfor help after 'assault' of colleague
OL,6,FIn 2017, a member of a research team
OL,7,Fthere smashed a colleague's room with
OL,8,Fan axe over an apparent love triangle,
OL,9,Faccording to a report to South
OL,10,FAfrica's Parliament. Lawmakers said it
OL,11,Fappeared the researchers were living
OL,12,Fin highly stressful conditions.
OL,14,FIn 2022 The US National Science
OL,15,FFoundation, published a report saying
OL,16,F59% of women in the U.S. program has
OL,17,Freported experiencing harassment or
OL,18,Fassault while on research trips in
OL,19,FAntarctica.
